title: 820 3536, Won't turn ON with original charge
message:
Hey, 

initial this board came with corrosion on c7210,c7215,r7210. i replace this components and the machine work's fine only with fake charge!! with original charge don't have green light and not charge! 

already replace Q7180 no changes! 

any idea??

title: 820 3536, Won't turn ON with original charge
message:
Original charger detects leakage...
Check voltages around Q7010.
Shorted D7010 can cause this.
Check R7012 on 200k scale onboard.

title: 820 3536, Won't turn ON with original charge
message: heeh, Replace D7010 and problem solve!!! You Rock with electronics! thank you
